Package management {{{1

Nix package manager
https://nixos.org/nix/
https://nixos.org/nix/manual/#ch-basic-package-mgmt
nix-channel --update
nix-env -qa #list packages or query by regex
nix-env -qas # package installation status
nix-env -u # upgrade all

